# SERVER Domain Rules
# ===================
# SvelteKit server: SSE streaming, session management, file watching.

SERVER_RULE_0=Server code lives in src/lib/server/ - session-manager.ts, file-watcher.ts, sse-manager.ts
SERVER_RULE_1=Sessions are stored as JSON files in a .plan-sessions/ directory alongside the source markdown
SERVER_RULE_2=File watcher (chokidar) monitors the markdown source and re-parses on change, pushing updates via SSE
SERVER_RULE_3=SSE manager maintains per-session client connections at GET /api/sse/[id]
SERVER_RULE_4=API routes: GET /api/sessions (list), GET /api/sse/[id] (stream), PUT /api/sessions/[id]/feedback, POST /api/sessions/[id]/approve, GET /api/sessions/[id]/versions
SERVER_RULE_5=hooks.server.ts initializes the file watcher and session manager on first request
SERVER_RULE_6=SvelteKit uses adapter-node for production builds, output in build/ directory
SERVER_RULE_7=Dev server runs on port 5199 (vite dev --port 5199)
